⍝ Format.tc
⍝ ═════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: Z character array; implicit ⎕PP
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ,1⌈⍴⍴B  (for simple B)
      ⍝ GNU APL uses ⍕ for Format (APL2 uses ⊕)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← ⍕B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,1⌈⍴⍴B
1
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← ⍕B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,1⌈⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: ¯1↓⍴Z ←→ ¯1↓⍴B  (for simple numeric array)
      (¯1↓⍴Z) ≡ ¯1↓⍴B
1
